  "2026-05-20T21:34:13.083Z",codex-manual-dogfood,"Manual dogfood evidence 2026-05-20: on temp item pm-j1m0, pm activity --limit 5 emitted full JSON-patch bodies for five entries; pm history pm-j1m0 --limit 20 emitted full patch bodies; pm history pm-j1m0 --compact --limit 20 emitted concise rows with op/author/patch_ops/changed_fields. Recommendation: make compact activity/history the default or add a brief default with explicit --full for patches; keep --compact for scriptable low-token review."
